texts.content: {"text":"7. U na semirtirmas va na ochlikni ketkazmasdir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,48]}]}

{"text":"8. O`shal kunda bir chehralar ne'mat xursandligi bilan to`ladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,64]}]}

{"text":"23. Illo, kim yuz o`girsa va kofir bo`lsa...","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,44]}]}

{"text":"24. Bas, uni Alloh katta azob bilan azoblaydir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,47]}]}

{"text":"26. So`ngra, albatta, ularning hisob-kitobi ham Bizda bo`ladir.","styles":[{"fill":{"content":{"render_type":"solid","solid":{"color":[1,1,1]}}},"font":{"path":"C:/Users/davro/AppData/Local/Microsoft/Windows/Fonts/Poppins-Regular.ttf","id":""},"size":9,"range":[0,63]}]}
